----------Behavior 1 ----------
Capitalize the first letter of a single word

Input: i
Output: I

----------Behavior 2----------
Capitalize the first letter of a multiple word string

Input: i am legend
Output: I Am Legend

----------Behavior 3----------
Do not capitalize designated words

Input: i am legend from the future
Output: I Am Legend from the Future

----------Behavoir 4----------
Capitalize designated words if they are the first word

Input: from i am legend
Output: From I Am Legend
